description:
The first day Arturo Sandoval landed in the United States, he played at Carnegie Hall. Listen to Sandoval talk about this experience and the great things it led to, including a Grammy Award for the live recording. 

Buy Arturo Sandoval's music at J.W. Pepper: https://www.jwpepper.com/sheet-music/search.jsp?redirect=2017-arturo-sandoval-music&pageview=grid-view&utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=jazz-100&utm_content=sandoval-video6
